Core Insight

Intelligence alone does not create durable capability.
Systems evolve through mechanisms that selectively reinforce useful pathways, preserve adaptive scars, increase plasticity under meaningful conditions, and convert repeated experience into stable structure.

Biological analogue: BDNF (Brain-Derived Neurotrophic Factor).
Pantheon analogue: a Neurotrophic Substrate — the growth medium beneath cognition, memory, and coordination.

